**媳婦：貞夫人{{link-ko|德水李氏|덕수 이씨}}，李㝡鎮次女<ref>{{cite web |title=《德水李氏世譜》（1931年版） |url=https://www.familysearch.org/search/catalog/1362971 |website=FamilySearch |access-date=2020-11-01 |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220103025/https://www.familysearch.org/search/catalog/1362971 |dead-url=no }}（丙編第91面）</ref>。和丈夫一起被流放（一說和女兒一起被貶為[[奴婢|官婢]]{{r|ko|page1=152}}）；夫妻兩人的葬地不明{{#tag:ref||name=il105 |group=註}}
